Class NamedVIPEvaluationStage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mesosphere.sdk.offer.evaluate.PortEvaluationStage
      • com.mesosphere.sdk.offer.evaluate.NamedVIPEvaluationStage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OfferEvaluationStage

    public class NamedVIPEvaluationStage
extends PortEvaluationStage
    This class evaluates an offer against a given PodInstanceRequirement for port resources as in PortEvaluationStage, additionally setting org.apache.mesos.Protos.DiscoveryInfo properly for DC/OS to pick up the specified named VIP mapping.
